            </p>
          </answer>
        </exercise>

        <exercise label="ex-surface-integral-flux-8">
          <statement>
            <p>
              <m>\surfaceS</m> is the closed surface composed of <m>\surfaceS_1</m>,
              part of the unit sphere and <m>\surfaceS_2</m>,
